Chemical composition. Flavonoids such as wagonin, baicalcin, and baicalin are the main components (
 Zobel et al., 1991; 
 Kovács et al., 2004; 
 Reichling and Galati, 2004; 
 Abdollahi Fard, 2012); essential oil (
 Fukuhara et al., 1987); terpenoids and steroids (e.g., β-caryophyllene, scutebaicalin, β-sitosterol) (
 Hussein et al., 1996).
